subSubSection.paragraph:
Slender Stylewort (
Erickson 1958
).

Some individuals on the following collections of 

L. sonderi

from South Australia and Victoria are infected by a smut that proliferates in the ovary, preventing the production of flowers and seed: 
R. Bates 32191
(AD); 
D. Hunt 2229
(AD); 
D. Hunt 2241
(AD, MEL); 
H.B. Williamson s.n.
(MEL 2256399, MEL 275679).
